{"service_name": "Value Based Programme and Project Management", "service_id": "6176842566336512", "company_name": "Selex ES Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Selex ES Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Value Based Programme and Project Management\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Selex ES offers Value based Programme and Project Management, a methodology to create Value for the Client based on BS EN 12973:2000 and gives an end to end framework for business improvement and consultancy problem solving which allows better business decisions with a clear auditable rationale.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Creation of Value for the Client\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     End to end framework for business improvement and problem solving\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Creative teamwork involving key employees and stakeholders\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Planning via a Work Plan\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Functional Analysis Systems Technique (FAST)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     How is it being delivered, how can it be improved\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can improve services, projects, processes and products\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Integrates a wide range of tools and techniques\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Programme management via a VBM steering group\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     British Standard BS EN 12973:2000 Value Management\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Clearer objectives, more closely aligned with business needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Better business decisions, with a clear rationale\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved team-working\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Facilitates innovation within the organisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improve Value for Money and reduced waste\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3583 to \u00a31326 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/6176842566336512-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/6176842566336512-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/6176842566336512-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/6176842566336512-terms-and-conditions.p